{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_51_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 ドーナツ作りのお勉強",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ミセドだーーーーーーーーーー！！\nこれ、ほんとにほんとにほんとにほんとなんだよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mister Dooooooooonut!!\nThis is really‚ really‚ really‚ really true‚ right!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 4.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとにほんとにほんとにほんとだよ\n編集部の人達が、ミセドに掛け合ってくれたみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's really‚ really‚ really‚ really true.\nIt looks like the editorial staff talked to Mister Donut for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2000000018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "一日店長さんをする、お誕生日の日に備えて\n今日はドーナツ作りを勉強させてもらうんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To prepare for your day as the store manager on your birthday‚\nToday‚ we're going to learn how to make donuts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 23.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "一日店長さんに、ドーナツ作り……！\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』、最高だよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being a one-day store manager and making donuts…!\n\"Miracle☆Idol Birthday!\" is the best~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 32.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、アイデアありがとう！\n猫ちゃんのお風呂より嬉しいかも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the idea‚ Nagisa-chan!\nIt's happier than a cat in a bath!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　見てー！　新商品のゼロカロリードーナツだ！\nあっちには、マスコットのもちもちウルフがいるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Look! Zero-calorie donuts‚ the new product!\nAnd over there‚ the fluffy mascot wolf!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さん、とっても楽しそうですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-san‚ you look like you're having so much fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "大好きなお店を貸切れるなんて、そうそうないからね\n芽衣ちゃーん、そろそろ撮影始まっちゃうよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's rare to get a chance to rent out your favorite store.\nMei-chan‚ the filming is about to start!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 58.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめ～ん、ちょっと待ってー！\nはい、スタッフさん、これお礼のドーナツです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry! Just a moment!\nHere‚ staff-san‚ these donuts are a thank you gift.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 60.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 66.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、嬉しいのは分かるけど\nそれ、お店の商品だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan‚ I know you're happy‚\nbut those are the store's products.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 72.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも芽衣、店長さんだから――\nあー！　店長さんになるのはお誕生日の日だった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But I'm the store manager—―\nAh—! I become the store manager on my birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あむあむ……ハッ！\nす、すみまふぇんっ、私も渡されて食べちゃいました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Munch munch… Huh!\nI-I'm sorry‚ I also ate the donut Mei gave me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 90.4666707356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……すっかり芽衣ちゃんのペースだね\n{user}さんに支払いお願いしとかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… we're completely in Mei-chan's pace.\nWe'll have to ask {user}-san to cover the cost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "生地は、最後まで切らずに残しておいて～……\nチョコにつければ、にゃにゃーん！　かんせーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave a part of the dough uncut…\nDip it in chocolate and… meow‚ meow! Done!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.9666798909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣さん、すっごく上手ですね！\n一度習っただけなのに、お店の人みたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-san‚ you're really good at this!\nYou look like a professional‚ even though it's your first time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 117.4333465576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、ミセドの動画で、ドーナツの作り方を\n紹介してるのがあってね。よく観てるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe~ In the Mister Donut video‚ they were showing how to make donuts‚\nand I've been watching it a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6893049331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんのお誕生日の時には\nドーナツ型のケーキを作ってくれたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Kotono-chan's birthday‚\nyou made a donut-shaped cake‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 131.4000132243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、喜んでくれて嬉しかったな～\nあ、そうだ！　チョコで、ここに目を描いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was so happy that she liked it!\nOh‚ that's right! I'll draw the eyes here with chocolate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.0000132243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "わ、このドーナツ、琴乃ちゃんの顔みたい\n可愛いな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ this donut looks like Kotono-chan.\nIt's cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 147.1666798909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "オリジナルドーナツですね！　こっちはすずちゃんで\n今作ってるのは……なんか変な顔ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An original donut! This one looks like Suzu-chan.\nAnd this one I'm making… has a funny face‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 156.7000132243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "これはね～、{user}さんドーナツ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the {user}-san donut!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7000132243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 159.7666798909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　へ、変な顔って言っちゃったの\nなしでお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? I-I didn't mean to say it had a funny face…\nPlease forgive me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ私は、ここをこうして……んしょ……あれ？\nうーん、羽の形にしたいのに……",
